ServiceRequestPatientGivenNameSearchParameter

Parameter patient.given:string

Searches for serviceRequest based on the patient's given name(s) eg) /ws/fhir2/{release}/ServiceRequest?patient.given={givenName}

ResourceServiceRequest
Expression(none)
Target ResourcesServiceRequest
MultiplesThe parameter cannot repeat or have multiple values
